descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see...a design with lines and empty squares.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...stays the same.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to...look at the color that form the design in the input.Find any empty areas of blocks that are enclosed  by the lines that form the main design, fill them yellow.You should end with the same original design from the input, but with the empty areas filled yellow.

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... A random green pattern
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size... Remains the same as the input size
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to... Fill each enclosed hole with yellow

descriptions.see_description: In the input, you should see... green pixels in a random pattern.
descriptions.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the input grid size.
descriptions.do_description: To make the output, you have to....copy the input grid and then fill in each area or pixel enclosed by green pixels with yellow.
